<h2 class="inline-title">Bitcoin is as easy as 
  <a class="inline-title circle-button" href="#demo-section-1">1</a>
  <a class="inline-title circle-button" href="#demo-section-2">2</a>
  <a class="inline-title circle-button" href="#demo-section-3">3</a>
</h2>

<p>Sending and receiving bitcoins is as simple as sending an email, the first thing we need is an <strong>address</strong></p><br>
<table id="demo-section-1" class="rounded-border">
  <td><label class="fake-circle-button"> 1 </label></td>
  <td valign="top"><%= image_tag "vault.png", alt: "Vault image" %></td>
  <td>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="small-10 columns text-left">
        <p>
          A Bitcoin <strong>address</strong> is the place where the bitcoins are actually stored<br>
          Like a transparent <strong>vault</strong>, the coins can only be moved by the <strong>key owner</strong> but the world can see what is inside<br>
          The address is a long sequence of letters and numbers and it looks like this:
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row text-center">
      <p>
        <strong class="title has-tooltip" title="You can generate and use as many addresses as desired at no cost">19s6nzcRuWWuXSikLNGmYsTdKkF8cBkFdJ</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
        <%= image_tag "QR_code.png", class: "has-tooltip", title: "This QR code represents the same address and can be easily read with a phone", width: 200, height: 200, alt: "QR code image" %><br><br>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="small-2 columns"></div>
      <div class="small-10 columns text-right">
        <p>
          The <strong>private key</strong> is the only key in the world that can transfer the bitcoins from the Bitcoin address<br>
          The private key is a long sequence of letters and numbers and it looks like this:
          <strong class="title has-tooltip" title="This key is unique for the address above">5J3p5psdFRh1XCBXsb8AbpaVTnwSjv5MMqt5ceAMMAHVeXhq8yi</strong>
        </p>        
      </div>
    </div>
  </td>
  <td valign="bottom"><%= image_tag "key.png", alt: "Private Key image" %></td>
</table>
